name: Arab Student Association
description: Our organization's mission and purpose is to represent the Arab students in a respectful and honorable manner and to build the social network between the Arab students to maximize their contribution to the campus diversity. The organization would actively engage community service activities and enrich the spirit of service within the members of the association. It would utilize the members' experience and knowledge for (Arabic-related) educational purposes, serving interested parties of the university.
